FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

# Book Management API

CRUD API for managing books with support for filtering and pagination.

---

## Books Collection [/books]

### List all books [GET]

Retrieve a list of all books with optional filtering by category.

+ Parameters
    + category (string, optional) - Filter by category
    + limit (number, optional, default: `10`) - Max results to return
    + offset (number, optional, default: `0`) - Results to skip

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (object)
        + books (array[Book]) - List of books
        + total (number) - Total book count

    + Body

            {
              "books": [
                {
                  "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
                  "title": "The Great Gatsby",
                  "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
                  "isbn": "9780743273565",
                  "publishYear": 1925,
                  "price": 10.99,
                  "category": "Classic"
                }
              ],
              "total": 1
            }

### Create a new book [POST]

Add a new book to the library.

+ Attributes (CreateBook)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "9780743273565",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Book)

    + Body

            {
              "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "9780743273565",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Error)

    + Body

            {
              "code": 400,
              "message": "Invalid request body"
            }

---

## Book Resource [/books/{id}]

### Get book by ID [GET]

Retrieve details of a specific book.

+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID (UUID format)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Book)

    + Body

            {
              "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "9780743273565",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 10.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Error)

    + Body

            {
              "code": 404,
              "message": "Book not found"
            }

### Update book [PUT]

Update information of an existing book.

+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID (UUID format)

+ Attributes (UpdateBook)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "title": "The Great Gatsby (Revised)",
              "price": 12.99
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Book)

    + Body

            {
              "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
              "title": "The Great Gatsby (Revised)",
              "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
              "isbn": "9780743273565",
              "publishYear": 1925,
              "price": 12.99,
              "category": "Classic"
            }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Error)

    + Body

            {
              "code": 404,
              "message": "Book not found"
            }

### Delete book [DELETE]

Remove a book from the library.

+ Parameters
    + id (string, required) - Book ID (UUID format)

+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Error)

    + Body

            {
              "code": 404,
              "message": "Book not found"
            }

---

# Data Structures

## Book (object)

Complete book information.

+ id: `123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000` (string, required) - Book ID
+ title: `The Great Gatsby` (string, required) - Book title
+ author: `F. Scott Fitzgerald` (string, required) - Author name
+ isbn: `9780743273565` (string, optional) - ISBN code
+ publishYear: `1925` (number, optional) - Publication year
+ price: `10.99` (number, optional) - Price in USD
+ category: `Classic` (enum[string], optional) - Book category
    + Members
        + `Classic`
        + `Fiction`
        + `Science`
        + `History`
        + `Biography`
        + `Technology`

## CreateBook (object)

Request body for creating a new book.

+ title: `The Great Gatsby` (string, required) - Book title
+ author: `F. Scott Fitzgerald` (string, required) - Author name
+ isbn: `9780743273565` (string, optional) - ISBN code
+ publishYear: `1925` (number, optional) - Publication year
+ price: `10.99` (number, optional) - Price in USD
+ category: `Classic` (enum[string], optional) - Book category
    + Members
        + `Classic`
        + `Fiction`
        + `Science`
        + `History`
        + `Biography`
        + `Technology`

## UpdateBook (object)

Request body for updating a book (all fields optional).

+ title: `The Great Gatsby (Revised)` (string, optional) - Book title
+ author: `F. Scott Fitzgerald` (string, optional) - Author name
+ isbn: `9780743273565` (string, optional) - ISBN code
+ publishYear: `1925` (number, optional) - Publication year
+ price: `10.99` (number, optional) - Price in USD
+ category: `Classic` (enum[string], optional) - Book category
    + Members
        + `Classic`
        + `Fiction`
        + `Science`
        + `History`
        + `Biography`
        + `Technology`

## Error (object)

Error response object.

+ code: `400` (number, required) - Error code
+ message: `Invalid request` (string, required) - Error message
+ details: `{}` (object, optional) - Additional error details
